## iOS Philosophy

This is the **focused** version. Core functionality optimised for:
- Small screen (6.1-6.9" phone, 11-13" iPad)
- Touch + gesture input (one-handed use)
- Siri and Shortcuts integration
- Glanceable information (widgets, Live Activities)
- Intermittent use (quick check, respond, leave)

**Design rule:** If it takes more than 2 taps to do the most common task, redesign it. iOS users are one-handed on a train.

